The kids in the movie weren't bad, tho, except for some parts. Anyway, good movie, fun movie. Probably the most unrealistic part was when Affleck brings Kendrick to a fancy hotel and she says, "I don't think I can afford this." Said no female ever, rofl. O, and she was cute as a button in this movie.
